com.mapgroup.to

Class PredSessionTO

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mapgroup.to.PredSessionTO
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class PredSessionTO
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class transmit information from the client to the server about the last prediction happened. It is necessary to generate PDF with the report of the prediction.
